        "headline": "USN-5376-5: Git regression",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "USN-5376-4 fixed a regression in Git. The update introduced a regression when specifying configuration includes due to additional restrictions. This update fixes the problem. We apologize for the inconvenience. Original advisory details: 俞晨东 discovered that Git incorrectly handled certain repository paths in platforms with multiple users support. An attacker could possibly use this issue to run arbitrary commands.",
          "lang": "en"
        },
