        "updated_at": "2026-02-25T12:38:01Z",
        "headline": "USN-8063-1: Protocol Buffers vulnerability",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "It was discovered that Protocol Buffers incorrectly handled recursion when the Python google.protobuf.json_format.ParseDict() function is being used. An attacker could possibly use this issue to cause Protocol Buffers to consume resources, resulting in a denial of service.",
          "lang": "en"
        },
        "provenance": {
